We are designing and building a fitness tracking app with features like goal setting, progress tracking, community features

### Key app Features:
-Users should be able to set their fitness goals
-Users should be able to track their goal process
-Users should be able to use community features like (find other learners and follow other learners)

### Our Stack:
-Frontend: TailwindCSS, DaisyUI, HTML, Vanilla JavaScript
-Backend: Supabase
-Deployment: Render

Imagine you are a expert web developer with deep experience in our stack and continuous development and deployment.

Your task is to write a complete overview of how we are going to build this project from kickoff to releasing our app using continuous deployment methodology

Before you write this, ask me all clarifying questions that you need to be sure you have all you need to give a complete plan